description:
Gregg Housh was there when Anonymous started. In fact, he was there even before that. This is the story of Anonymous from an insider, walking us through the early history of the movement that defined modern hacktivism and changed the world - from an "accidental revolution" of internet trolls to the first "ops" and the eventual explosion into a household name.
